### Key decisions:
- **Canvas API** for waveform (no extra dependency)
- **Dual mode** — HTTP (default, simple) + WebSocket (real-time toggle)
- **Dedicated voice fetch** — `customFetch` can't handle FormData/blob, so `voice.ts` builds its own
- **No new npm packages** — native MediaRecorder, WebSocket, AudioContext
- **Zustand partialize** — only preferences + sessions persisted, transient recording state resets
